6086	   a spec defect.  The driver unconditionally calls ZopfliLZ77Greedy whose replaced
6087	   contract demands a fresh s->lmc, store->size == 3 and inend == 8; but the code
6088	   immediately above produces s->lmc == NULL (ZopfliInitBlockState is called with
